   "source": "<ROUTINE LIGHTHOUSE-LOCK-PSEUDO (\"OPTIONAL\" (PARG <>))\n\t <COND (<==? .PARG ,M-NAME>\n\t\t<PUTP ,PSEUDO-OBJECT ,P?SDESC \"lock\">)\n\t       (<VERB? PICK>\n\t\t<TELL \"You try for a while, but the lock won't give.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? UNLOCK>\n\t\t<TELL-NO-KEY>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? MUNG>\n\t\t<TELL \n\"You find that the door and lock withstand your attempts.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? LOCK>\n\t\t<TELL-ALREADY \"locked\">\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>>"
