   "source": "<ROUTINE DIR-PRINT (DIR \"AUX\" (CNT 0) TBL (DRY <>))\n\t #DECL ((DIR CNT) FIX)\n\t <COND (<NOT .DIR>\n\t\t<TELL \"out of view\">\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<G? <GETP ,HERE ,P?LINE> ,BACK-ALLEY-LINE-C>\n\t\t<SET TBL ,NAUTICAL-DIR-STRINGS>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<SET TBL ,DIR-STRINGS>\n\t\t<SET DRY T>)>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<==? <GET .TBL .CNT> .DIR>\n\t\t\t<COND (<AND .DRY\n\t\t\t\t    <NOT <EQUAL? .DIR ,P?UP ,P?DOWN>>>\n\t\t\t       <TELL \"the \">)>\n\t\t\t<PRINT <GET .TBL <+ .CNT 1>>>\n\t\t\t<RTRUE>)>\n\t\t <SET CNT <+ .CNT 1>>>>"
